There’s the Gregorian calendar, and then there’s the fashion calendar. According to the style schedule, spring is solidly upon us. One need only to look at the dizzying array of goodies now arriving in stores. Yet despite the flood of tantalizing warm-weather options, most of us are living with temperatures that willfully go against our fashion fantasies. Often, when we’re still in coats and boots, the only weather-appropriate way to dip a toe into the new season is with a fresh top. And since a statement blouse, knit or hoodie happens to be the cornerstone of one of the season’s most striking looks, there is really no reason to wait any longer to splurge. Here, the best trends to try for your top half.